      "text": "Ad click Event Aggregation system",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Ad click Event Aggregation system",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "Do2gETu_P95eMmO07jSOD",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 261,
      "y": 233.5,
      "width": 564.0596313476562,
      "height": 1775,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bhP",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 2129570059,
      "version": 1293,
      "versionNonce": 1914910085,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1783769412430,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Clarifications:\n\nq. whats a ad click event agrregateion system?\nWe get events, they need to be aggregated and displayed\n\nq. imp features?\nyes\nwe want aggregation on \n- number of events for an ad in last 1 min\n- sorted top 100 ads in last m mins\n- filter by ip, tenent on both above queries\n\nq. multi tenant system or in house?\nin house\n\nq. aggregation types?\nall\n- sum\n- avg\n- percentiles p50, p95, p99\n\nq. how doe we get events?\nin a csv file or stream of events\n\nq. how to display the aggregations?\nin a dashboard\n\nq. DAU?\n1 billion DAU\n\nq. any other considerations?\nhandle duplicate events\nhandle late events\n\nFunctional req:\n1. Ad click evnet ingestion\n2. Event aggregation\nwe want aggregation on \n- number of events for an ad in last 1 min\n- sorted top 100 ads in last m mins\n- filter by ip, tenent on both above queries\n3. Aggregation display on dashboard\n\nNFR:\n- Available : SLA 99.9\n- Scalable\n- Reliable and Fault tolerent\n- low latency \nEnd 2 end ingetion : 1 min\nAgrregation display : 1 sec\n\nBack of the enevelope calc:\n1 billion DAU * 1 ad a day\n= 10^9 event click a day / 10^5\n= 10000 event click per sec\n\n100k companies with 100 ads ongoing\n= 10m ads ongoing\n\ndashboard views = \n100k * 100 times a day\n= 10 m views a day\n= 100 rps\n\nstorage :\n1 billion click a day\n* 100 bytes\n= 10^9 * 100 bytes\n= 10^8 kb\n= 100 gb per day\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Clarifications:\n\nq. whats a ad click event agrregateion system?\nWe get events, they need to be aggregated and displayed\n\nq. imp features?\nyes\nwe want aggregation on \n- number of events for an ad in last 1 min\n- sorted top 100 ads in last m mins\n- filter by ip, tenent on both above queries\n\nq. multi tenant system or in house?\nin house\n\nq. aggregation types?\nall\n- sum\n- avg\n- percentiles p50, p95, p99\n\nq. how doe we get events?\nin a csv file or stream of events\n\nq. how to display the aggregations?\nin a dashboard\n\nq. DAU?\n1 billion DAU\n\nq. any other considerations?\nhandle duplicate events\nhandle late events\n\nFunctional req:\n1. Ad click evnet ingestion\n2. Event aggregation\nwe want aggregation on \n- number of events for an ad in last 1 min\n- sorted top 100 ads in last m mins\n- filter by ip, tenent on both above queries\n3. Aggregation display on dashboard\n\nNFR:\n- Available : SLA 99.9\n- Scalable\n- Reliable and Fault tolerent\n- low latency \nEnd 2 end ingetion : 1 min\nAgrregation display : 1 sec\n\nBack of the enevelope calc:\n1 billion DAU * 1 ad a day\n= 10^9 event click a day / 10^5\n= 10000 event click per sec\n\n100k companies with 100 ads ongoing\n= 10m ads ongoing\n\ndashboard views = \n100k * 100 times a day\n= 10 m views a day\n= 100 rps\n\nstorage :\n1 billion click a day\n* 100 bytes\n= 10^9 * 100 bytes\n= 10^8 kb\n= 100 gb per day\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
