    {
      "id": "3Tv_-oljcZykAiy5hMFuW",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1049.339502421988,
      "y": 856.5406640987859,
      "width": 557.859619140625,
      "height": 675,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bhr",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 226748805,
      "version": 588,
      "versionNonce": 1496391717,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1783770003607,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Communication:\n1. API\n2. Events ( preferred)\n\nFlows:\n\nEvent ingestion:\n1. Get raw data from streams or batches\n2. Add data in kafka\n3. Ingestion svc reads the data and writes to DB\nwhich db?\nwrite heavy workload : \nSQL: not preferred\nNoSQL: cassandra\n\nAggregation:\n1. Aggregation svc consumes data from kafka\n2. Perform aggregation\n3. Persist aggregated data\nwhich db?\nwrite and read heavy:\ncassandra or postgres\nopt for postgres\n\nDisplay flow\n1. Admin user calls API from query svc\n2. Query svc gets aggregated data from aggregation svc",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Communication:\n1. API\n2. Events ( preferred)\n\nFlows:\n\nEvent ingestion:\n1. Get raw data from streams or batches\n2. Add data in kafka\n3. Ingestion svc reads the data and writes to DB\nwhich db?\nwrite heavy workload : \nSQL: not preferred\nNoSQL: cassandra\n\nAggregation:\n1. Aggregation svc consumes data from kafka\n2. Perform aggregation\n3. Persist aggregated data\nwhich db?\nwrite and read heavy:\ncassandra or postgres\nopt for postgres\n\nDisplay flow\n1. Admin user calls API from query svc\n2. Query svc gets aggregated data from aggregation svc",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
